Package fi.tuni.swdesign.group3.gui.view

Class CheckBoxTreePopulator

java.lang.Object
fi.tuni.swdesign.group3.gui.view.CheckBoxTreePopulator
Direct Known Subclasses:
CombinedDataCBTPopulator, RoadDataCBTPopulator, WeatherDataCBTPopulator
public abstract class CheckBoxTreePopulator extends Object
An abstract base class for populating the checkbox treeview in the different datatabs.
Author:
Lauri Puoskari
